Feature 1 Favorites¶

Welcome to the documentation for Feature 1 Favorites.

This feature provides tools for creating personalized bundles of favorite items. It includes modules for: - Data input/output (DataIO). - Data transformations (Transformer). - A recommendation pipeline (FavoriteService).
